## Design Sections → Data Sources

| Stitch Section | Data Source | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| **DLD Live Feed** (left overlay) | `trpc.marketIntel.evidence.list` | Latest evidence records, sorted by date |
| **Market Status** ("Strong Bullish") | `trpc.analytics.getTrends` | Trend direction from analytics |
| **Top Benchmarks** (right panel) | `trpc.design.getAreaBenchmarks` | Top 3 areas by sale P50 |
| **Price/SqFt by Tier** (right panel) | `trpc.design.getAreaBenchmarks` | Grouped by tier from benchmark data |
| **Yield Forecast** (right panel) | `trpc.design.getAreaBenchmarks` | Yield data from benchmarks |
| **Dubai Map** (center) | Static map image + heatmap overlay | Decorative with data pins |
| **Filters bar** | UI state | Asset class, timeframe toggles |

## Proposed Changes

### Client Pages

#### [NEW] [MarketIntelligence.tsx](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/client/src/pages/market-intel/MarketIntelligence.tsx)

New premium page with the Stitch design pattern:
- **Header**: "Market Intelligence & Evidence" + live sync indicator + region selector
- **Filters Bar**: Asset class chips, timeframe selector, Map/Grid toggle
- **Map Area** (left 60%): Dubai satellite map background with heatmap glow spots, data pins with tooltips, and DLD Live Feed glass panel overlay with latest evidence records
- **Market Status** glass card: Bullish/Bearish indicator + 24h volume
- **Right Panel** (right 40%): Top Benchmarks (top 3 areas), Price/SqFt by Tier bars, Yield Forecast chart
- All data from existing tRPC queries — no new backend needed

